# Tool Registry

> Zeus consults this file before invoking or creating any tool. If a tool is not here, it does not exist. If a tool is created, it must be registered here before use.

---

## How to Read This Registry

| Column | Meaning |
|---|---|
| Name | Tool identifier used in delegation briefs |
| Type | `skill` (reusable logic), `hook` (event-triggered), `command` (explicit invocation), `subagent` (delegated reasoning) |
| Path | Location in project |
| Agent | Which agent owns/uses this tool |
| Purpose | What it does in one sentence |
| Status | `active`, `draft`, `deprecated` |

